        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
            <p>CD must be happy about the tendency toward acceptance of his views, though it is regrettable that France is backward in this regard.</p>
            <p>His own work goes slowly, but he still hopes his work on artificially produced monstrosities will help to answer the question of the origin of species.</p>
        </abstract>
